org.ndnx.ndn.protocol
Class PublisherID

java.lang.Object
  org.ndnx.ndn.impl.encoding.GenericXMLEncodable
      org.ndnx.ndn.protocol.PublisherID
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<PublisherID>, XMLEncodable
public class PublisherID
extends GenericXMLEncodable
implements XMLEncodable, Comparable<PublisherID>, Serializable

Helper wrapper class for publisher IDs. This encodes and decodes as one of 4 inline options, one of which also appears separately as the PublisherPublicKeyDigest.
